Purpose:

This folder contains all the Fragment classes.
A Fragment represents a portion of the user interface within an activity
and it is often used for modular UI components that can be reused across multiple activities.

What to include:

* Fragment classes representing different parts of the UI
* Code that handles fragment lifecycle and UI logic
* Navigation between fragments (if needed)

Examples:

* HomeFragment.kt
* DetailFragment.kt
* ProfileFragment.kt